name: deleteAccountResult
title: With Connect, You Can Delete Accounts You Manage
description: With connect, you can delete accounts you manage. Accounts created using test-mode keys can be deleted at any time. Standard accounts created using live-mode keys cannot be deleted. Custom or express accounts created using live-mode keys can only be deleted once all balances are zero. If you want to delete your own account, use the account information tab in your account settings instead
